	</li>
	<li class="grouped other-questions" style="display: none;">
		<ul>
			<li>
				<p id="same-amount-label">Are you expecting to get the same amount each week?</p>
				<ul class="radio" id="195e794e8cf852d4e6744b01a7b182d7cb2b348be899b163064a7c7e19d8a50a">
					<li>
					    <input type="radio" id="195e794e8cf852d4e6744b01a7b182d715823206cd78b8b2f2daebc27fad3cad" name="195e794e8cf852d4e6744b01a7b182d7cb2b348be899b163064a7c7e19d8a50a" value="yes">
					    <label for="195e794e8cf852d4e6744b01a7b182d715823206cd78b8b2f2daebc27fad3cad">Yes</label>
